# CODEOWNERS uses last-match-wins, not most-specific-wins. The supply-chain
# sensitive paths are pinned to the same team today; if `*` is ever broadened
# to a wider audience, workflow/Dependabot/CI changes stay locked to the
# maintainer team without a separate CODEOWNERS edit.
*                       @microsoft/module-info-maintainers
.github/workflows/      @microsoft/module-info-maintainers
.github/dependabot.yml  @microsoft/module-info-maintainers
.github/CODEOWNERS      @microsoft/module-info-maintainers
